rian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1847]] {{ill|December 22|ja|12月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ōtsuki Fumihiko|ja|大槻文彦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a linguist and author of "Gengai" (died [[1928]]). * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1861]] {{ill|December 16|ja|12月16日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ochiai Naofumi|ja|落合直文|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a waka poet (died [[1903]]). * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1863]] {{ill|December 25|ja|12月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Shiga Jūkō|ja|志賀重昂|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a geographer and politician (died [[1927]]).
