egoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1861]] {{ill|December 16|ja|12月16日}}) – {{ill|Ochiai Naofumi|ja|落合直文}}, a waka poet (died [[1903]]). * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1863]] {{ill|December 25|ja|12月25日}}) – {{ill|Shiga Jūkō|ja|志賀重昂}}, a geographer and politician (died [[1927]]).
