* {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1867]] {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|qq=|12=draft}}) – In the [[Ōmiya Incident]], both {{ill|Sakamoto Ryōma|ja|坂本龍馬|qq=|12=draft}} and {{ill|Nakaoka Shintarō|ja|中岡慎太郎|qq=|12=draft}} were attacked; Ryōma died on that day, and Shintarō died three days later.
* {{ill|Meiji era|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1872]] {{ill|December 15|ja|12月15日|qq=|12=draft}}) – The {{ill|National Bank Ordinance|ja|国立銀行条例|qq=|12=draft}} was enacted.
* In Meiji 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} 1872, 12月15日) – The year of the accession of {{ill|Emperor Jimmu|ja|神武天皇|qq=|12=draft}} was established as the Japanese era of [[Kigen]] ({{ill|Jimmu Tennō Sokui Kigen|ja|神武天皇即位紀元|1=Japanese imperial year|qq=|12=draft}}).

