== Events == * {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|qq=|qq=draft}} 19th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1614]] {{ill|December 15|ja|12月15日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – During the {{ill|Osaka Winter Campaign|ja|大坂冬の陣|qq=|qq=draft}}, the army of {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=|qq=draft}} set out to attack {{ill|Osaka Castle|ja|大坂城|qq=|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1867]] {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – In the [[Ōmiya Incident]], both {{ill|Sakamoto Ryōma|ja|坂本龍馬|qq=|qq=draft}} and {{ill|Nakaoka Shintarō|ja|中岡慎太郎|qq=|qq=draft}} were attacked; Ryōma died on that day, and Shintarō died three days later. * {{ill|Meiji era|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1872]] {{ill|December 15|ja|12月15日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – The {{ill|National Bank Ordinance|ja|国立銀行条例|qq=|qq=draft}} was enacted. * In Meiji 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} 1872, 12月15日) – The year of the accession of {{ill|Emperor Jimmu|ja|神武天皇|qq=|qq=draft}} was established as the Japanese era of [[Kigen]] ({{ill|Jimmu Tennō Sokui Kigen|ja|神武天皇即位紀元|1=Japanese imperial year|qq=|qq=draft}}).
