== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft}} 14th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1586]] {{ill|December 25|ja|12月25日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Yoshikawa Motoharu|ja|吉川元春|qq=|qq=draft}}, a Sengoku-period warrior and the second son of {{ill|Mōri Motonari|ja|毛利元就|qq=|qq=draft}} (born [[1530]]). * {{ill|Jōō|ja|承応|qq=|qq=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1654]] {{ill|January 3|ja|1月3日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Matsunaga Sadatoku|ja|松永貞徳|qq=|qq=draft}}, a haiku poet and classicist (born [[1571]]). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1867]] {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Sakamoto Ryōma|ja|坂本龍馬|qq=|qq=draft}}, a Bakumatsu statesman (born [[1836]]).
