{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十一月十五|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 11월 15일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar November|qq=}} '''November 15''' is the 15th day of the month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November (Lunisolar)|qq=}} the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senshō|qq=}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 19th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1614]] {{ill|December 15|ja|12月15日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 15|qq=}}) – During the {{ill|Osaka Winter Campaign|ja|大坂冬の陣|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Osaka Winter Campaign|qq=}}, the army of {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ieyasu|qq=}} set out to attack {{ill|Osaka Castle|ja|大坂城|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Osaka Castle|qq=}}. * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keiō|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1867]] {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 10|qq=}}) – In the [[Ōmiya Incident]], both {{ill|Sakamoto Ryōma|ja|坂本龍馬|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakamoto Ryōma|qq=}} and {{ill|Nakaoka Shintarō|ja|中岡慎太郎|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nakaoka Shintarō|qq=}} were attacked; Ryōma died on that day, and Shintarō died three days later. * {{ill|Meiji era|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1872]] {{ill|December 15|ja|12月15日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 15|qq=}}) – The {{ill|National Bank Ordinance|ja|国立銀行条例|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/National Bank Ordinance|qq=}} was enacted. * In Meiji 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} 1872, 12月15日) – The year of the accession of {{ill|Emperor Jimmu|ja|神武天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Jimmu|qq=}} was established as the Japanese era of [[Kigen]] ({{ill|Jimmu Tennō Sokui Kigen|ja|神武天皇即位紀元|1=Japanese imperial year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jimmu Tennō Sokui Kigen|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese imperial year|qq=}}).
== Births == * {{ill|Eishō|ja|永正|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eishō|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1507]] {{ill|December 18|ja|12月18日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 18|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ōuchi Yoshitaka|ja|大内義隆|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōuchi Yoshitaka|qq=}}, a daimyō (died [[1551]]). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kansei|qq=}} 9th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1798]] {{ill|January 1|ja|1月1日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/January 1|qq=}}) – {{ill|Utagawa Kuniyoshi|ja|歌川国芳|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Utagawa Kuniyoshi|qq=}}, an ukiyo-e artist (died [[1861]]). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunsei|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1819]] {{ill|December 31|ja|12月31日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 31|qq=}}) – {{ill|Miyaji Tsunetoki|ja|宮地常磐|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Miyaji Tsunetoki|qq=}}, head of the Chōkō-tenma Shrine (died [[1890]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanu