== Events == * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|慶長|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 19th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1614]] {{ill|December 15|ja|12月15日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 15|qq=}}) – During the {{ill|Osaka Winter Campaign|ja|大坂冬の陣|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Osaka Winter Campaign|qq=}}, the army of {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ieyasu|qq=}} set out to attack {{ill|Osaka Castle|ja|大坂城|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Osaka Castle|qq=}}. * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keiō|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1867]] {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 10|qq=}}) – In the [[Ōmiya Incident]], both {{ill|Sakamoto Ryōma|ja|坂本龍馬|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakamoto Ryōma|qq=}} and {{ill|Nakaoka Shintarō|ja|中岡慎太郎|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nakaoka Shintarō|qq=}} were attacked; Ryōma died on that day, and Shintarō died three days later. * {{ill|Meiji era|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1872]] {{ill|December 15|ja|12月15日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 15|qq=}}) – The {{ill|National Bank Ordinance|ja|国立銀行条例|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/National Bank Ordinance|qq=}} was enacted. * In Meiji 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} 1872, 12月15日) – The year of the accession of {{ill|Emperor Jimmu|ja|神武天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Jimmu|qq=}} was established as the Japanese era of [[Kigen]] ({{ill|Jimmu Tennō Sokui Kigen|ja|神武天皇即位紀元|1=Japanese imperial year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jimmu Tennō Sokui Kigen|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese imperial year|qq=}}).
== Births == * {{ill|Eishō|ja|永正|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eishō|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1507]] {{ill|December 18|ja|12月18日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 18|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ōuchi Yoshitaka|ja|大内義隆|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōuchi Yoshitaka|qq=}}, a daimyō (died [[1551]]). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kansei|qq=}} 9th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1798]] {{ill|January 1|ja|1月1日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/January 1|qq=}}) – {{ill|Utagawa Kuniyoshi|ja|歌川国芳|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Utagawa Kuniyoshi|qq=}}, an ukiyo-e artist (died [[1861]]). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunsei|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1819]] {{ill|December 31|ja|12月31日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 31|qq=}}) – {{ill|Miyaji Tsunetoki|ja|宮地常磐|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Miyaji Tsunetoki|qq=}}, head of the Chōkō-tenma Shrine (died [[1890]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1836]] {{ill|January 3|ja|1月3日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/January 3|qq=}}) – {{ill|Sakamoto Ryōma|ja|坂本龍馬|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakamoto Ryōma|qq=}}, a statesman of the Bakumatsu period (died [[1867]]). * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōka|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1847]] {{ill|December 22|ja|12月22日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 22|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ōtsuki Fumihiko|ja|大槻文彦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtsuki Fumihiko|qq=}}, a linguist and author of "Gengai" (died [[1928]]). * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunkyū|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1861]] {{ill|December 16|ja|12月16日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 16|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ochiai Naofumi|ja|落合直文|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ochiai Naofumi|qq=}}, a waka poet (died [[1903]]). * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunkyū|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1863]] {{ill|December 25|ja|12月25日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 25|qq=}}) – {{ill|Shiga Jūkō|ja|志賀重昂|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shiga Jūkō|qq=}}, a geographer and politician (died [[1927]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 14th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1586]] {{ill|December 25|ja|12月25日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 25|qq=}}) – {{ill|Yoshikawa Motoharu|ja|吉川元春|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yoshikawa Motoharu|qq=}}, a Sengoku-period warrior and the second son of {{ill|Mōri Motonari|ja|毛利元就|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mōri Motonari|qq=}} (born [[1530]]). * {{ill|Jōō|ja|承応|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jōō|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1654]] {{ill|January 3|ja|1月3日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/January 3|qq=}}) – {{ill|Matsunaga Sadatoku|ja|松永貞徳|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Matsunaga Sadatoku|qq=}}, a haiku poet and classicist (born [[1571]]). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keiō|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1867]] {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 10|qq=}}) – {{ill|Sakamoto Ryōma|ja|坂本龍馬|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakamoto Ryōma|qq=}}, a Bakumatsu statesman (born [[1836]]).
